@startuml

|Author|
start
:Write Article Draft;
  :Self-Correction & Formatting;
if (Content Ready?) then (yes)
    :Submit for Review;
else (no)
    :Fix Typos;
endif


|Editor|
:Receive Draft;
if (Meets Standards?) then (yes)
  :Approve Article;
else (no)
  :Reject with Feedback;
endif

|System|
:Run SEO & Plagiarism Check;
if (Checks Passed?) then (yes)
  fork
    :Publish on Website;
    :Generate PDF Version;
  fork again
    :Update Search Index;
    :Archive in Database;
  end fork
  :Push Social Media API;
else (no)
  :Log Technical Error;
endif
:Send Status Notification;

|Author|
:View Confirmation;
stop
@enduml
